PATENT CLARIFICATION

This open-source software contains ONLY the publicly released, non-patented 
mathematical modules of Abhishek’s Theory of Everything (ATOE).

The following advanced capabilities are explicitly NOT included and remain 
protected under Abhishek’s filed patents:

- Advanced FDE topology selection
- Knot clumping and collective multi-knot behaviour
- Dynamic self-adjusting resonance tuning
- Energy harvesting efficiency predictions
- Battery, motor, remote actuator, quantum computing, biological, and fusion modules

Any commercial hardware, devices, or products based on the complete ATOE 
framework (resonators, batteries, motors, actuators, etc.) require a separate 
licensing agreement with the inventor.

